{"tid":1949861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全部都要】習近平：既要保證生產 還要保證身體健康","createTime":"2020-03-30T03:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T05:16:13.000Z","uid":51271,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d405b44fed0ebe0de8a0a32f4251569ff92d28b1","tid":1949861,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:05:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>屌你老母撚屌，當日你唔隱暪最多停產一兩個月，而家全球同你埋單停半年都有份</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1585536989284&amp;issue=20200330\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1585536989284%26issue%3D20200330&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq1UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=1c1a63f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1585536989284&amp;issue=20200330</a><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情全球爆發，重挫環球經濟。為使經濟重回正軌，內地多個城市已陸續復工復產，據《央視》報道，中國國家主席習近昨日到寧波北崙大碶高端汽配模具園區視察及與工人會面，並表示「在防控疫情的情況下，積極地開展復工復產，既要保證生產任務，還要保證身體健康。」"},{"pid":"ea0d547740a0f68bd0c4f833c2c89f94a603ab07","tid":1949861,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:06:16.000Z","msg":"今日下午有大量還押手足上庭跪求聲援<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949806</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2b0e9e14bc03871bece5f899353aa6436d21a016","tid":1949861,"uid":219537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:06:26.000Z","msg":"傻hi黎既"},{"pid":"905129367eb66e979cce1273960cf8a460c27a5c","tid":1949861,"uid":42364,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:08:21.000Z","msg":"又要威<br />\n又要唔戴套屌閪"},{"pid":"dc513eabb4bcbe4daf877237fdee80519933b932","tid":1949861,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"905129367eb66e979cce1273960cf8a460c27a5c","tid":1949861,"uid":42364,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTi